{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "f1a2b3c4-d5e6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "Flights Booking App",
		"description": "Comprehensive API collection for the Flights Booking App microservices.\n\n## Architecture\n- **API Gateway** (port 3001) — Auth, users, and proxy to downstream services\n- **Flights Booking Service** (port 3002) — Bookings and seat reservations\n- **Flights Creation Service** (port 3003) — Flights, airplanes, airports, cities, airlines\n- **Flights Searching Service** (port 3004) — Flight search with caching\n- **Notifications Service** (port 3005) — Email notifications via RabbitMQ\n\n## Proxy Routes (via Gateway)\nThe API Gateway proxies requests to downstream services:\n- `/flightsCreationService/*` → Flights Creation Service\n- `/flightsSearchingService/*` → Flights Searching Service\n- `/flightsBookingsService/*` → Flights Booking Service",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:3001",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "authToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
